How to Run the Detector
Step 1 — Download the ZIP

From the repo:
https://github.com/ccievks/Ccievks-Threatintel-Repo/tree/main/Shai-hulud-2.0

Step 2 — Extract
Unzip the file into any working directory.

Step 3 — Install dependencies
Inside the extracted folder:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 4 — Run the scanner
Point it at your project directory:

python shai_hulud_detector.py --path /your/project/root

Step 5 — Review results
The scanner will fetch live intelligence from all 5 threat intel sources and report:

Newly compromised packages
Packages found in your environment
Detected malicious version ranges
Recommended remediation actions
This gives instant clarity on whether your project or CI pipeline is exposed.
